description: Spectacular evening of Latin social dancing with a Masquerade theme. Doors open at 4:15 PM, beginner lessons followed by social dancing. Features Salsa, Bachata, Kizomba, and Merengue. Prizes for best-dressed.
Latin social dancing with dance styles varying each month. Open to all. $15 General Admission, $12 Students.
